nodes.bodyText:
In ZkHelixManager, the sharding building is done like this:
  private String buildShardingKey() {
    return _clusterName.charAt(0) == '/' ? _clusterName : "/" + _clusterName;
  }

I figured the state model factory should do the same. It doesn't hurt to check anyways.

